\id 2TH Matupi Chin Standard Bible
\h 2THESSALONIKA
\toc1 2THESSALONIKA
\toc2 2Thessalonika
\toc3 2Th
\mt1 THESSALONIKA CAPAT
\mt3 A Pabae Nah
\mt4 (Second Letter to the Thessalonians)
\is2 THESSALONIKA CAPAT
\im Thessalonika hlangboel rhoek he tangnah neh lungnah dongah a rhoeng uh he ni Paul loh Pathen a uemnah lamhmacuek (chapter 1.3). Amih te ngaihmangnah muep om dae Pathen kah datatnah pawt tih noemcaihnah ni tila amih taengah a thui (1.4,5).
\ip A ngen long tah Paul kah capat dongah Khrih a pabae halo coeng baboel tah tah a ti uh (2.2). Tedae hlang ang bangla om uh boeh a ti nah (2.3).
\ip Paul loh yalpo bingak he a ngaih moenih (3.6-10), ol aka ngai pawt te a then la rhalrhing uh a ti nah.
\iot Sawt Yoeinah
\io1 Kuttuknah \ior (1. 1,2)\ior*
\io1 Boeipa halo vaengah tiktamnah \ior (1. 3-12)\ior*
\io1 Boeipa ha mael hlan \ior (2. 1-12)\ior*
\io1 Uepomnah \ior (2. 13-17)\ior*
\io1 Thangthuinah neh bibinah \ior (3. 1-15)\ior*
\io1 Hnukkhueng kah thangthuinah \ior (3. 16-18)\ior*
\c 1
\s1 Uemnah Ol
\p 
